        }
      },
      "id": "add-to-archival",
      "name": "Add to Letta Archival",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1020, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Letta Memory Update Workflow\n\nThis workflow updates the hydra-steward agent's archival memory with:\n\n1. **Alertmanager Webhooks** - Alerts are logged to agent memory\n2. **Custom Events** - Manual memory updates via webhook\n3. **Scheduled Checks** - Periodic consolidation entries\n\n**Webhook URL:** `http://192.168.1.244:5678/webhook/letta-memory`\n\n**POST Body Examples:**\n```json\n// Custom event\n{\"event\": \"Container restart\", \"details\": {\"name\": \"hydra-mcp\"}}\n\n// Direct text\n{\"text\": \"Important note about the cluster\"}\n```",
        "height": 400,
        "width": 340
      },
      "id": "sticky-note",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [20, 160]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "options": {}
      },
